Salvatore Emma, Jr.

Age : 57Public asset : 101,439 USDLinked companies :  Micron Solutions Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Salvatore Emma, Jr., is on the Board of Directors at Arrhythmia Research Technology, Inc. Mr. Emma was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Micron Products, Inc. and Controller by Kervick Enterprises, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from Fitchburg State University.



